## Testing

Run the complete test suite:

```bash
pytest
```

Run one module of tests:

```bash
pytest tests/test_constant_rate.py
```

## Reproducibility Notes

- Randomized routines expose seed arguments where practical.
- The package functions are split from plotting so numerical results can be
	tested independently of visualization.
